title: Shankly's 2011 Mixtapes - The Ones I Missed
description:
Thanks to all the bloggers and others that do end-of-year lists and helped the Great Shankly discover more music at the end of 2011 than he did during the year itself. 

Thanks especially to Dandelion Radio for the definitive end of year list - their Festive 50 - most of which can be found below. 

The 2012 mixtapes are up next...
